### 13.3 Code Review Focus Areas

**Review for:**

1. ✅ Proper TypeScript usage (no `any`, no inline assertions)
2. ✅ Blade component usage (no custom UI)
3. ✅ Test coverage (especially for analytics)
4. ✅ Error handling and Sentry logging
5. ✅ Performance considerations (memoization, lazy loading)
6. ✅ Accessibility (proper ARIA labels, semantic HTML)
7. ✅ Component structure (proper file organization)
8. ✅ Naming conventions followed
9. ✅ No class components or compose pattern
10. ✅ Analytics properly integrated and tested

